### 3. APPCC Service (`src/modules/appcc/appcc.service.spec.ts`)

**Root Cause:** DTO enums not exported from `appcc.dto.ts` file.

**Fixes Applied:**

1. Exported enums in `src/modules/appcc/dto/appcc.dto.ts`:
   - ControlType
   - CleaningFrequency
   - PestType
