└── Menu Engineering Module
    ├── Stars analysis (high popularity, high profit)
    ├── Plowhorses analysis (high profit, low popularity)
    ├── Puzzles analysis (high popularity, low profit)
    ├── Dogs analysis (low popularity, low profit)
